msgctxt "68_Chigusa"
msgid "So the package here will tell me how you really feel about\\r\nme? What's that supposed to mean?"
msgstr "¿Así que el paquete que hay aquí me dirá lo que\\r\nrealmente sientes por mí? ¿Qué quiere decir?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "80_Kiryu"
msgid "I couldn't say. I guess you'll find out once you hand that\\r\nslip to the man behind the counter."
msgstr "Ni idea. Supongo que lo descubrirás cuando le des ese\\r \nrecibo al hombre detrás del mostrador."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "92_Chigusa"
msgid "...Right. Let's go inside."
msgstr "...Ya. Entremos."

